  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Warehouse cum Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>Warehouse cum Van Driver</strong></p><h2>Job Summary</h2><p>The Warehouse cum Van Driver is responsible for supporting daily warehouse operations and ensuring timely, safe delivery and collection of goods. This role combines hands-on warehouse duties with driving responsibilities and requires reliability, attention to detail, and a strong sense of responsibility.</p><h2>Key Responsibilities</h2><h3>Warehouse Operations</h3><ul><li><p>Receive, check, and store incoming goods accurately</p></li><li><p>Pick, pack, and prepare items for delivery according to delivery orders</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper inventory records and assist with stock counts</p></li><li><p>Ensure the warehouse is kept clean, organised, and safe at all times</p></li><li><p>Assist with loading and unloading of goods</p></li><li><p>Follow workplace safety and operational procedures</p></li></ul><h3>Driving & Delivery</h3><ul><li><p>Deliver and collect goods using company van according to scheduled routes</p></li><li><p>Ensure timely, accurate, and safe delivery of items</p></li><li><p>Check delivery items against delivery orders before dispatch</p></li><li><p>Handle goods with care to prevent damage during transport</p></li><li><p>Perform basic vehicle checks (fuel, tyre pressure, cleanliness)</p></li><li><p>Report any vehicle issues, accidents, or delays promptly</p></li></ul><h2>Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>Valid <strong>Singapore Class 3 driving licence</strong> (clean driving record preferred)</p></li><li><p>Prior experience in <strong>warehouse operations and/or delivery driving</strong> is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Physically fit and able to carry or move goods when required</p></li><li><p>Familiar with Singapore roads and navigation</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and follow instructions accurately</p></li><li><p>Basic understanding of inventory and delivery documentation</p></li><li><p>Reliable, punctual, and responsible</p></li></ul><h2>Working Conditions</h2><ul><li><p>Based in warehouse with regular driving duties</p></li><li><p>May require overtime or flexible hours depending on operational needs</p></li></ul>",
